{"tid":585033,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"若要有創意 要投鄧家彪","createTime":"2018-03-08T09:47:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T06:50:09.000Z","uid":141400,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fe3a6d912a19c5cae38bbb42f67b0d53b0024dab","tid":585033,"uid":141400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"北區太多人與車<br />\n乘客用腳行到夜<br />\n害怕下班等很久的車<br />\n條街水貨滿瀉<br />\n<br />\n家彪要選代議者<br />\n郵費又竟會貼漏些<br />\n拍過的片 卻又撤去 最熟悉咀臉<br />\n<br />\n拿着兜去行乞選票<br />\n亦有簡單問好 不過少<br />\n然後再次企對面 就如王國興<br />\n<br />\n巴士有事從未出頭<br />\n若靠工會點知佢 掉轉槍頭<br />\n但見加薪方案已由賺變扣<br />\n你也會想過絕望叫它狗<br />\n<br />\n即炒兩字情絕不留<br />\n望鏡9up 的聲線 我最難受<br />\n待補選完結  使乜驚圍屌<br />\n<br />\n最多選票就贏了<br />\n<br />\n改《彌敦道》"},{"pid":"4c318728822679b1cd4287d8f7db0b5aec915ff8","tid":585033,"uid":1245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:50:40.000Z","msg":"爭屎 乞衣仔"},{"pid":"3e6516b40fbcfba2e936acb40a9d040befe9c3f7","tid":585033,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7ca08811bd160e39c7c667db873ca777be91bac","tid":585033,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:56:51.000Z","msg":"此帖必火"},{"pid":"305704de54262e9b0df968e84be8ff911b0886db","tid":585033,"uid":38041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:59:13.000Z","msg":"推到有人唱"},{"pid":"c089602108787cd03b1a616b8cf5207bb76d7257","tid":585033,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T13:39:42.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"4bc2b29b749dfb8399541fef89aa81ec0f2d6824","tid":585033,"uid":74458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T13:43